{"id":907,"parent_id":905,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":907,"title":"Joel 2","subtitle":"","short_title":"Joel","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 2"],[".studySummary",["i","War and desolation will precede the Second Coming—The sun and the moon will be darkened—The Lord will pour out His Spirit upon all flesh—There will be dreams and visions."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.1","order":"02.30.002.60825"},["b","1"],"Blow ye the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"trumpet"],"in Zion, and sound an alarm in my holy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"mountain"],": let all the inhabitants of the land tremble: for the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"cometh, for",["i","it is"],"nigh at hand;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.2","order":"02.30.002.60826"},["b","2"],"A day of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"darkness"],"and of gloominess, a day of clouds and of thick darkness, as the morning spread upon the mountains: a great people and a strong; there hath not been ever the like, neither shall be any more after it,",["i","even"],"to the years of many generations."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.3","order":"02.30.002.60827"},["b","3"],"A fire",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"devoureth"],"before them; and behind them a flame burneth: the land",["i","is"],"as the garden of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Eden"],"before them, and behind them a desolate wilderness; yea, and nothing shall escape them."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.4","order":"02.30.002.60828"},["b","4"],"The appearance of them",["i","is"],"as the appearance of horses; and as horsemen, so shall they run."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.5","order":"02.30.002.60829"},["b","5"],"Like the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"noise"],"of chariots on the tops of mountains shall they leap, like the noise of a flame of fire that devoureth the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"stubble"],", as a strong people set in battle array."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.6","order":"02.30.002.60830"},["b","6"],"Before their face the people shall be much pained: all faces shall gather",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"blackness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.7","order":"02.30.002.60831"},["b","7"],"They shall run like mighty men; they shall climb the wall like men of war; and they shall march every one on his ways, and they shall not break their ranks:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.8","order":"02.30.002.60832"},["b","8"],"Neither shall one thrust another; they shall walk every one in his path: and",["i","when"],"they fall upon the sword, they shall not be wounded."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.9","order":"02.30.002.60833"},["b","9"],"They shall run to and fro in the city; they shall run upon the wall, they shall climb up upon the houses; they shall enter in at the windows like a thief."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.10","order":"02.30.002.60834"},["b","10"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"earth"],"shall quake before them; the heavens shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"tremble"],": the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sun"],"and the moon shall be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"dark"],", and the stars shall withdraw their shining:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11","order":"02.30.002.60835"},["b","11"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall utter his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"voice"],"before his army: for his camp",["i","is"],"very great: for",["i","he is"],"strong that executeth his word: for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"great"],"and very terrible; and who can",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_11d"},"abide"],"it?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.12","order":"02.30.002.60836"},["b","12"],"¶Therefore also now, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"turn"],"ye",["i","even"],"to me with all your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"heart"],", and with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"fasting"],", and with weeping, and with mourning:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.13","order":"02.30.002.60837"},["b","13"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"rend"],"your heart, and not your garments,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"and"],"turn unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God: for he",["i","is"],"gracious and merciful, slow to anger, and of great",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"kindness"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"repenteth"],"him of the evil."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.14","order":"02.30.002.60838"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Who"],"knoweth",["i","if"],"he will return and repent, and leave a blessing behind him;",["i","even"],"a meat offering and a drink offering unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God?"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.15","order":"02.30.002.60839"},["b","15"],"¶Blow the trumpet in Zion, sanctify a fast, call a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"solemn assembly"],":"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.16","order":"02.30.002.60840"},["b","16"],"Gather the people, sanctify the congregation, assemble the elders, gather the children, and those that suck the breasts: let the bridegroom go forth of his chamber, and the bride out of her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"closet"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.17","order":"02.30.002.60841"},["b","17"],"Let the priests, the ministers of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"weep"],"between the porch and the altar, and let them say, Spare thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"people"],", O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and give not thine heritage to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"reproach"],", that the heathen should rule over them: wherefore should they say among the people, Where",["i","is"],"their God?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.18","order":"02.30.002.60842"},["b","18"],"¶Then will the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"jealous"],"for his land, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"pity"],"his people."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.19","order":"02.30.002.60843"},["b","19"],"Yea, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will answer and say unto his people, Behold, I will send you corn, and wine, and oil, and ye shall be satisfied therewith: and I will no more make you a reproach among the heathen:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.20","order":"02.30.002.60844"},["b","20"],"But I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"remove"],"far off from you the northern",["i","army,"],"and will drive him into a land barren and desolate, with his face toward the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"east"],"sea, and his hinder part toward the utmost sea, and his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"stink"],"shall come up, and his ill savour shall come up, because he hath done great things."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.21","order":"02.30.002.60845"},["b","21"],"¶Fear not, O land; be glad and rejoice: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will do great things."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.22","order":"02.30.002.60846"},["b","22"],"Be not afraid, ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"beasts"],"of the field: for the pastures of the wilderness do spring, for the tree beareth her fruit, the fig tree and the vine do yield their strength."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.23","order":"02.30.002.60847"},["b","23"],"Be glad then, ye children of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"Zion"],", and rejoice in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God: for he hath given you the former rain moderately, and he will cause to come down for you the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"rain"],", the former rain, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"latter"],"rain in the first",["i","month."]],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.24","order":"02.30.002.60848"},["b","24"],"And the floors shall be full of wheat, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"fats"],"shall overflow with wine and oil."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.25","order":"02.30.002.60849"},["b","25"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"restore"],"to you the years that the locust hath eaten, the cankerworm, and the caterpiller, and the palmerworm, my great army which I sent among you."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.26","order":"02.30.002.60850"},["b","26"],"And ye shall eat in plenty, and be satisfied, and praise the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, that hath dealt wondrously with you: and my people shall never be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"ashamed"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.27","order":"02.30.002.60851"},["b","27"],"And ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"midst"],"of Israel, and",["i","that"],"I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, and none else: and my people shall never be ashamed."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.28","order":"02.30.002.60852"},["b","28"],"¶And it shall come to pass afterward,",["i","that"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"pour out"],"my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"spirit"],"upon all flesh; and your sons and your daughters shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"prophesy"],", your",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"old"],"men shall",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_28e"},"dream"],"dreams, your young men shall see",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_28f"},"visions"],":"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.29","order":"02.30.002.60853"},["b","29"],"And also upon the servants and upon the handmaids in those days will I pour out my spirit."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.30","order":"02.30.002.60854"},["b","30"],"And I will shew",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"wonders"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"heavens"],"and in the earth, blood, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"fire"],", and pillars of smoke."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.31","order":"02.30.002.60855"},["b","31"],"The sun shall be turned into darkness, and the moon into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"blood"],", before the great and the terrible",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"come."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.32","order":"02.30.002.60856"},["b","32"],"And it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"whosoever shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"call"],"on the name of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_32b"},"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"]],"shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_32c"},"delivered"],": for in",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_32d"},"mount"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_32e"},"Zion"],"and in",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_32f"},"Jerusalem"],"shall be",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_32g"},"deliverance"],", as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath said, and in the",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_32h"},"remnant"],"whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","i"],["a",{"href":"fn_32i"},"call"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.1a","order":"02.30.002.60857"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","shofar,"]],"or ram’s horn."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.1b","order":"02.30.002.60859"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.17"},"Joel 3:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/12.3.2-4"},"2 Ne. 12:3 (2–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/30.15.12-18"},"30:15 (12–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.1c","order":"02.30.002.60861"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.2a","order":"02.30.002.60863"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.12.11-19"},"Ezek. 34:12 (11–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.18.18-20"},"Amos 5:18 (18–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.3a","order":"02.30.002.60865"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.21"},"D&C 29:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.3b","order":"02.30.002.60867"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eden"},"TG Eden"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.5a","order":"02.30.002.60869"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/9.9"},"Rev. 9:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.5b","order":"02.30.002.60871"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.15.15,23"},"1 Ne. 22:15 (15, 23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/15.24"},"2 Ne. 15:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.6.4,6"},"26:6 (4, 6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.24.23-24"},"D&C 64:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.64"},"133:64"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.6a","order":"02.30.002.60873"},["b","6a"],"Hebrew idiom meaning “gloom.”",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.21"},"Jer. 8:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/nahum/2.10"},"Nahum 2:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.10a","order":"02.30.002.60875"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-destiny-of"},"TG Earth, Destiny of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.10b","order":"02.30.002.60877"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.18"},"D&C 43:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.118"},"84:118"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.10c","order":"02.30.002.60879"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.14"},"D&C 29:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.42"},"45:42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.87"},"88:87"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.49"},"133:49"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-m/1.33"},"JS—M 1:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.10d","order":"02.30.002.60881"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.10"},"Isa. 13:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/32.7"},"Ezek. 32:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.29"},"Matt. 24:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11a","order":"02.30.002.60883"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.21"},"D&C 35:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/43.18.17-25"},"43:18 (17–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.90"},"88:90"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.50.50-52"},"133:50 (50–52)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11b","order":"02.30.002.60885"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.7"},"Jer. 30:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11c","order":"02.30.002.60887"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/34.8"},"D&C 34:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"11d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.11d","order":"02.30.002.60889"},["b","11d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2"},"Mal. 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.12a","order":"02.30.002.60891"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/30.